"```sql\nSELECT DISTINCT client.client_id\nFROM client\nJOIN disp ON client.client_id = disp.client_id\nJOIN card ON disp.disp_id = card.disp_id\nWHERE card.type = 'junior' AND card.issued >= '1997-01-01';\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects distinct client IDs from the `client` table by joining it with the `disp` (disposition) table and the `card` table. It filters for cards of type 'junior' that were issued on or after January 1, 1997."